  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Blue Gem/DST</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\">\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p>The <b>Blue Gem</b> is an item used to craft several <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Magic\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Magic\">Magical</a> Items. It can be used to craft the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice_Staff\" title=\"Ice Staff\">Ice Staff</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Chilled_Amulet\" title=\"Chilled Amulet\">Chilled Amulet</a> and <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Purple_Gem\" title=\"Purple Gem\">Purple Gem</a>.\n</p><p>Blue Gems can be used to turn <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Chester\" title=\"Chester\">Chester</a> into <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Snow_Chester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Snow Chester\">Snow Chester</a> by placing at least one in each of his inventory slots on a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Full_Moon\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Full Moon\">Full Moon</a>, granting him slower food spoilage like a mobile <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice_Box\" title=\"Ice Box\">Ice Box</a>. \n</p><p>Blue Gems can be used to craft a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Salt_Box\" title=\"Salt Box\">Salt Box</a> and inserted into <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cratered_Moonrock\" title=\"Cratered Moonrock\">Cratered Moonrocks</a> to acquire a Blue <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Moonlens\" title=\"Moonlens\">Moonlens</a>. They can also be used to power <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Winona%27s_G.E.M.erator\" title=\"Winona&#x27;s G.E.M.erator\">Winona&#x27;s G.E.M.erator</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Blue_Gem/DST#Gathering\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Gathering</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Blue_Gem/DST#Usage\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Usage</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Blue_Gem/DST#Trivia\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Trivia</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Blue_Gem/DST#Gallery\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Gallery</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Gathering\">Gathering</span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dragonfly\" title=\"Dragonfly\">Dragonfly</a> and the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Malbatross\" title=\"Malbatross\">Malbatross</a> drop Blue Gems upon death.</li>\n<li>Blue <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Gem_Deer\" title=\"Gem Deer\">Gem Deer</a> will also drop a Blue Gem if killed or if Klaus is dead.</li>\n<li>Blue Gems have a 0.04% chance to be dropped by <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Tumbleweed\" title=\"Tumbleweed\">Tumbleweeds</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sunken_Chest\" title=\"Sunken Chest\">Sunken Chests</a> can contain a Blue Gem, with equal chance of a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Red_Gem\" title=\"Red Gem\">Red Gem</a> in its place.</li>\n<li>Blue Gems can be crafted by Wilson if he has obtained &quot;<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Transmute_Gems_I\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Transmute Gems I\">Transmute Gems I</a>&quot;.</li>\n<li>15% chance to be found in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ornate_Chest\" title=\"Ornate Chest\">Ornate Chest</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Usage\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Icon_Tools\" title=\"Icon Tools\"><img alt=\"Icon Tools.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Icon_Tools.png/32px-Icon_Tools.png?f672d4\" width=\"32\" height=\"39\"></a> Usage</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Blue_Gem\" title=\"Blue Gem\"><img alt=\"Blue Gem.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Blue_Gem.png?51fe73\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Red_Gem\" title=\"Red Gem\"><img alt=\"Red Gem.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Red_Gem.png?a91ebd\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Prestihatitator\" title=\"Prestihatitator\"><img alt=\"Prestihatitator.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Prestihatitator.png/42px-Prestihatitator.png?4c1c7b\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Purple_Gem\" title=\"Purple Gem\"><img alt=\"Purple Gem.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Purple_Gem.png?ca6f08\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Blue_Gem\" title=\"Blue Gem\"><img alt=\"Blue Gem.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Blue_Gem.png?51fe73\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Spear\" title=\"Spear\"><img alt=\"Spear.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Spear.png?63081f\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Prestihatitator\" title=\"Prestihatitator\"><img alt=\"Prestihatitator.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Prestihatitator.png/42px-Prestihatitator.png?4c1c7b\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice_Staff\" title=\"Ice Staff\"><img alt=\"Ice S