ki.gg/wiki/Wilson\" title=\"Wilson\"><img alt=\"Wilson Portrait.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Wilson_Portrait.png/64px-Wilson_Portrait.png?ecb2be\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></td><td class=\"dark-invert\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Transmute_Gems_III\" title=\"Transmute Gems III\"><img alt=\"Transmute Gems III.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Transmute_Gems_III.png?347fb8\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Placeholder\" title=\"Placeholder\"><img alt=\"Placeholder.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Placeholder.png/32px-Placeholder.png?210282\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Trivia</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Blue Gems were introduced in the <i>A Winter&#x27;s Tale</i> update.</li>\n<li>Blue Gems used to have the same shape as Red Gems.</li>\n<li>The old Blue Gem appearance can be seen on the Ultimate Survival Inventory poster sold on Klei&#x27;s official merch store.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Gallery\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Blueprint\" title=\"Blueprint\"><img alt=\"Blueprint.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Blueprint.png/32px-Blueprint.png?80b6b5\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Gallery</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Blue_Gem_emoji_from_official_Klei_Discord_server.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Medal blue emoji from official Klei Discord server.\"><img alt=\"Medal blue emoji from official Klei Discord server.\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Blue_Gem_emoji_from_official_Klei_Discord_server.png/120px-Blue_Gem_emoji_from_official_Klei_Discord_server.png?7d2f87\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Medal blue emoji from official Kl